{"id": 1229, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得适合和爸妈一起看的电影有哪些？", "description": "每隔两周我们会推出“给电影人性化分类系列”征集，本周是，你觉得和你爸妈一起看什么电影既不尴尬又开心？", "record_count": 2054, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160919164856wEcag5UW3nsKJfPr.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-10-09T03:00:20Z", "options": [{"id": 122112, "content": "1942，活着，无人区，拯救大兵瑞恩", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 787922}, {"id": 122113, "content": "星际迷航等的美国科幻大片", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 787927}, {"id": 122114, "content": "贺岁片", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 584951}, {"id": 122370, "content": "除了动画电影，其他都得自己提前看一遍没有尴尬镜头的才能跟父母一起再看一遍。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 466835}, {"id": 122115, "content": "人在囧途", "image": null, "praise_count": 40, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 446828}, {"id": 127235, "content": "喜剧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 807482}, {"id": 122116, "content": "喜剧。比如唐人街探案，人在囧途之港囧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 787949}, {"id": 122117, "content": "智取威虎山、澳门风云", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 777423}, {"id": 122118, "content": "贺岁片", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 719355}, {"id": 124166, "content": "在3刷魔兽的时候，我带上了我妈去看，让她知道，我背后纹身的意义！为了部落！", "image": "img/option/option/20161015013205GzsVSY9KZilPyAfa.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 795420}, {"id": 122119, "content": "叙述表达负面信息较少的  父母总是希望自己的孩子充满朝气 多多关注正能量 而且这类电影往往能带动和谐融洽的气氛", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 204479}, {"id": 122120, "content": "取决于共同欣赏角度。科幻我觉得老少通吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 778133}, {"id": 122121, "content": "《消失的爱人》，这样他们就不会催你结婚了。", "image": "img/option/option/20161009142209qy81csS9FOjM4Pbm.jpg", "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 56933}, {"id": 122633, "content": "婆媳家庭喜剧电影", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 789292}, {"id": 122122, "content": "不靠各种噱头，故事本身能打动人的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 787084}, {"id": 122123, "content": "音乐之声", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 281894}, {"id": 124171, "content": "周星驰的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 795539}, {"id": 122124, "content": "湄公河行动", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 787972}, {"id": 122125, "content": "贺岁档吧。和自己妈一起看过一次港囧，开头那点都很尴尬。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 779095}, {"id": 122126, "content": "纪录片，不但种类多，而且可以有所讨论。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 787977}, {"id": 122127, "content": "宫崎骏的动画电影", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 781105}, {"id": 122128, "content": "不知道等我们老了会不会害怕和子女一起看少儿不宜的片子！", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 671390}, {"id": 122132, "content": "根本没有", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 771964}, {"id": 122133, "content": "活着。我爸看了第二天给我说还看昨天那个 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 114275}, {"id": 122134, "content": "超级英雄电影啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 609627}, {"id": 122137, "content": "湄公河行动类的军事片，或者入泰囧般的喜剧片。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 783641}, {"id": 122138, "content": "恐怖片 商业大片", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 780212}, {"id": 122139, "content": "当年看了蓝星人觉得3D效果做得太好了，于是二刷带亲爹亲妈去了，结果俺爹依然睡着，对，每次带他们看电影他都睡着（手动撇嘴）", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 752659}, {"id": 122140, "content": "场面比较大的科幻片吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 780844}, {"id": 122141, "content": "韩国电影，《我爱你》，讲述了两对老夫妻晚年的故事，老年人间的爱情故事更动人。也更容易引起彼此曾经等我回忆", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 582735}, {"id": 122142, "content": "每次都踩雷，《女朋友，男朋友》《两小无猜》", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 747758}, {"id": 122655, "content": "只要没有吻戏，床戏……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 789743}, {"id": 122144, "content": "没电影可看", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 396392}, {"id": 122145, "content": "战争片，一致对外；喜剧片，其乐融融", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 788111}, {"id": 122657, "content": "恐怖片?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 789751}, {"id": 122146, "content": "什么都可以啊，有做爱场景我和我爸也一起看（。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 436982}, {"id": 122147, "content": "电影院上好看的电影 我都会拉我老妈去看 嗯 好像 没有特别不能看的..我们口味比较接近", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 773309}, {"id": 122148, "content": "与历史有关的题材，类似唐山大地震", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 722337}, {"id": 129318, "content": "国语的！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 817314}, {"id": 122151, "content": "三傻大闹宝莱坞", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 731285}, {"id": 126761, "content": "没有适合的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 679121}, {"id": 122155, "content": "忠犬八公，没啥三观分歧，老少咸宜，就是有点催泪。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 468703}, {"id": 122667, "content": "剧情片", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 789774}, {"id": 128555, "content": "动画片", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 814636}, {"id": 122156, "content": "只要我们都想看的，完全都可以一起看！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 45006}, {"id": 122157, "content": "动画片", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 661073}, {"id": 122158, "content": "搞定岳父大人、智取威虎山", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 692867}, {"id": 122670, "content": "《钢琴家》《星际穿越》", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 783868}, {"id": 122159, "content": "地道战", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 436707}, {"id": 124466, "content": "老版搞笑电影", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 796478}]}